wards.<\/p>","pc_margin_top":"50px","pc_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"16475013125523c92a":{"type":"graphic-module","blocks":{"164750131287ba8e58-0":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/953ebbc1f2f5775c228625e1c716cf87_9f54a571-71c7-48ec-9559-5c6866e477ac.png","main_title":"750 W","text":"Rear Hub Motor"}},"164750131287ba8e58-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/dcbf258b7e33f36ca3423eee233866fa_de432622-0eb2-47a9-abe8-ae126cd45e78.png","main_title":"85N.m","text":"Motor Torque"}},"164750131287ba8e58-2":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/c5b9a1702888b8b61400b8ec135d2fdf_d822fd5c-b9f0-4407-ab8b-041e1a3c26fe.png","main_title":"48V -13 Ah","text":"Lithium-lon Battery"}},"164750131287ba8e58-3":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/92ccb5073072aeb08280d30f5618bb0c_e21f446c-da51-483a-8ffa-7f3685c9247a.png","main_title":"300 lbs","text":"Payload Capacity"}}},"block_order":["164750131287ba8e58-0","164750131287ba8e58-1","164750131287ba8e58-2","164750131287ba8e58-3"],"settings":{"max_width":"1140px","main_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/M-17.jpg","pc_margin_top":"50px","pc_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"1647501322c3877c5d":{"type":"slide-bar","blocks":{"1647501322f515ca86-0":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6484.jpg","text":"<strong>Step-thru Frame Design<\/strong><br>Step-thru frame design on MF-17 allows riders ride on the bike more easily. The standover height of MF-17 is only 19.5 inch."}},"1647501322f515ca86-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6438.jpg","text":"<strong>Suspension Front Fork <\/strong><br>We developed and produced Maxfoot suspension forks in cooperation with well-known manufacturers. While ensuring beautiful design, we pay more attention to the rider's experience. The long-distance suspension stroke allows the MF-18 P to filter out most of the bumps, ensuring a comfortable riding experience for the rider. Therefore, with the Maxfoot suspension fork, the MF-18 P can conquer many terrains."}},"1647501322f515ca86-2":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6655.jpg","text":"<strong>Thoughtful Big Curved Handlebar <\/strong><br>Curved Handlebar aluminum handlebars allow adjustment to support various arm lengths and a more laid back riding position. During riding, the curved handlebar allows the rider to ride in a comfortable position. you will not feel uncomfortable because of the sitting position even when traveling long distances."}},"71f02c94-2f73-4176-916b-ec2f9f4b9e79":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6037.jpg","text":"<strong>Thick Padded Saddle, Designed For Comfort <\/strong><br>Adjustable thick Padded Saddle can greatly alleviate your discomfort caused by a long journey and all-round buffering allows you to feel what is the comfortable riding. You can adjust it according to the height. Appropriate height for this bike is 5'4''-6'3''."}},"a916a8f2-a026-4a64-905a-766cafc72164":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6585.jpg","text":"<strong>Maxfoot 750W Hub Motor<\/strong><br>The motor of MF-18 P is Maxfoot motor developed by Maxfoot and a well-known manufacturer. While guaranteeing the quality of the motor, it also improves the performance of the motor. At a rated power of 750W, the Maxfoot motor can output at least 1050W of power. There will be no security risks due to its high performance."}},"43d8ef9b-7150-472f-a62e-bcbac2c16d46":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6486.jpg","text":"<strong>Maxfoot Lithium Battery<\/strong><br>In order to ensure the long-range of the MF-18 P, Maxfoot teamed up with well-known manufacturers to develop a 13Ah Maxfoot large-capacity battery. As the energy support of MF-18 P, we attach great importance to its quality. We need